Week 2

Building blocks of Oops

Class , Object   - template/blueprint is

Candle maker - vessel, wax,

Constructor - object initialization, developers to set up object state
              default (no-arg) | parameterized constructor

this keyword - Refers to current object / Current class instance variable


Oops - not 100%

Encapsulation  - wrapping data and methods in single unit
Abstraction    - class without providing implementation, leaving that to the subclass (Abstract class,Interface)
Polymorphism   - multiple forms (compile-time/method overloading , run-time/method riding)
Inheritance    - Inherit (method+variables) to another class extends
                 single inheritance, multilevel, hierachical, multiple(interface)

 